                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "345"
                    },
                    "date": 1959
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  The description",
                " of the detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "An investigation  was  carried  out  of  the  angular",
                " distribution of photoneutrons with energies above 10",
                " MeV  emitted  by Be-9,  C-12 and Al-27 targets under",
                " the  irradiation  by   88   MeV   end-point   energy",
                " bremsstrahlung. The energy spectrum of photoneutrons",
                " emitted at the angle of 75  degrees  from  C-12  was",
                " also  investigated and from the data thus obtained a",
                " comparison  is  made   of   the   photoneutron   and",
                " photoproton yields in the same energy intervals. The",
                " angular distribution results are compared  with  the",
                " quasi-deutron   model   and   the  model  of  direct",
                " resonance nuclear photoeffect. Qualitative agreement",
                " with the quasi-deutron model has been obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
