          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To determine the photoneutron spectrum the groups  of",
                " proton  recoils  formed in the converter by neutrons",
                " from 1 MeV-wide range around the mean energies  E(i)",
                " were graphically found.  On the basis of such graphs",
                " constructed for the neutrons energies E(i) with  the",
                " step  of  1 MeV the number of recoil protons in each",
                " energy interval may be  calculated  by  summing  the",
                " number  of  neutrons  multiplied by some coefficient",
                " over  all  possible  values  of  E(i).  The   energy",
                " distribution  of  neutrons  which  took  place after",
                " calculations  the   experimental   distribution   of",
                " protons   was  regarded  as  the  real  photoneutron",
                " spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For (a)  the  thickness  of the converter and (b) the",
                " cross section of (n,p)-scattering were made."
              ]
            }
          ],
